# The start symbol is START.

# These two rules are required; choose their weights carefully!
99 START -> S1
1 START -> S2

# This is a very, very, very simple grammar to get you started.

1 S1 -> NP VP .

1 VP -> VerbT NP

20 NP -> Det Nbar
1 NP -> Proper

20 Nbar -> Noun
1 Nbar -> Nbar PP

1 PP -> Prep NP

###

S1 -> {SingPhrase | PluralPhrase}
NP -> {SingNP | PluralNP }


AdjPhrase -> {CommaAdj | AndAdj}
AdjPhrase -> {Adj | CompAdj | SuperAdj}

CommaAdj -> CommaAdj Comma CommaAdj
CommaAdj -> {Adj | CompAdj | SuperAdj}

AndAdj -> AndAdj And AndAdj
AndAdj -> {Adj | CompAdj | SuperAdj}

SingPhrase -> SingNP SingVP

SingNP -> Det (AdjPhrase) Noun
SingNP -> ProperNoun

SingVP -> VerbT NP

PluralPhrase -> PluralNP PluralVP
PluralNP -> (PluralDet) (AdjPhrase) PluralNoun
PluralNP -> PluralProperNoun

PluralVP -> VerbT NP

